plain":"count     280.00\nmean    16621.01\nstd      4371.80\nmin      8525.00\n25%     13468.75\n50%     15845.00\n75%     18634.75\nmax     32685.00\nName: upah, dtype: float64"},"metadata":{}},{"name":"stdout","text":"\n💰 Upah Rata-Rata Tertinggi: Rp 32,685\n💰 Upah Rata-Rata Terendah: Rp 8,525\n💰 Mean Upah Rata-Rata: Rp 16,621\n","output_type":"stream"}],"execution_count":9},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"**Interpretasi statistik deskriptif**\n\nPada data UMP, nilai **mean lebih tinggi daripada median**, yang mengindikasikan distribusi cenderung **miring ke kanan (right-skewed)**. Artinya ada beberapa provinsi dengan UMP sangat tinggi yang mendorong rata-rata nasional naik, terutama provinsi dengan pusat kegiatan ekonomi besar atau biaya hidup tinggi.\n\nSementara itu, rentang nilai yang lebar antara minimum dan maksimum menunjukkan bahwa kondisi ketenagakerjaan antarprovinsi di Indonesia masih cukup beragam. Dengan kata lain, rata-rata nasional penting sebagai gambaran umum, tetapi belum cukup untuk mewakili kondisi semua provinsi secara setara.\n","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"## 3. Data Cleaning dan Preprocessing","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"# Cek missing values\nprint(\"🔍 Pengecekan Missing Values:\")\nprint(\"\\nUMP Dataset:\")\nprint(df_ump.isnull().sum())\nprint(f\"Total missing: {df_ump.isnull().sum().sum()}\")\n\nprint(\"\\nRata-Rata Upah Dataset:\")\nprint(df_upah.isnull().sum())\nprint(f\"Total missing: {df_upah.isnull().sum().sum()}\")\n\n# Cek duplikat\nprint(f\"\\n🔍 Duplikat di UMP: {df_ump.duplicated().sum()}\")\nprint(f\"🔍 Duplikat di Rata-Rata Upah: {df_upah.duplicated().sum()}\")\n\n# Normalisasi nama provinsi (uppercase dan strip whitespace)\ndf_ump['provinsi'] = df_ump['provinsi'].str.upper().str.strip()\ndf_upah['provinsi'] = df_upah['provinsi'].str.upper().str.strip()\n\nprint(\"\\n✓ Data cleaning selesai!\")","metadata":{"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2026-04-06T00:59:54.492689Z","iopub.execute_input":"2026-04-06T00:59:54.493025Z","iopub.status.idle":"2026-04-06T00:59:54.518037Z","shell.execute_reply.started":"2026-04-06T00:59:54.492988Z","shell.execute_reply":"2026-04-06T00:59:54.517106Z"},"trusted":true},"outputs":[{"name":"stdout","text":"🔍 Pengecekan Missing Values:\n\nUMP Dataset:\nprovinsi     0\ntahun        0\nump         24\ndtype: int64\nTotal missing: 24\n\nRata-Rata Upah Dataset:\nprovinsi    0\ntahun       0\nupah        0\ndtype: int64\nTotal missing: 0\n\n🔍 Duplikat di UMP: 0\n🔍 Duplikat di Rata-Rata Upah: 0\n\n✓ Data cleaning selesai!\n","output_type":"stream"}],"execution_count":10},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"**Interpretasi data cleaning**\n\nTahap cleaning menunjukkan bahwa kualitas data secara umum sudah baik karena **tidak ada duplikat** dan hanya ada **24 nilai hilang pada kolom UMP**. Karena jumlah missing relatif kecil dibanding total observasi, dampaknya terhadap gambaran umum tren nasional kemungkinan terbatas.\n\nMeski begitu, keberadaan missing value tetap penting dicatat. Jika nilai yang hilang terkonsentrasi pada provinsi atau tahun tertentu, maka pembacaan detail untuk kombinasi provinsi-tahun tersebut perlu dilakukan dengan lebih hati-hati.\n","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"## 4. Analisis Tren UMP","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"### 4.1 Evolusi UMP Nasional (2002-2022)\n","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"# Hitung rata-rata UMP per tahun\nump_yearly = df_ump.groupby('tahun')['ump'].agg(['mean', 'median', 'min', 'max']).reset_index()\n\n# Visualisasi\nfig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(16, 8))\n\nax.plot(ump_yearly['tahun'], ump_yearly['mean'], marker='o', linewidth=2.5, \n        label='Rata-rata UMP', color='#2E86AB', markersize=8)\nax.plot(ump_yearly['tahun'], ump_yearly['median'], marker='s', linewidth=2.5, \n        label='Median UMP', color='#A23B72', markersize=8)\n\n# Fill area antara min dan max\nax.fill_between(ump_yearly['tahun'], ump_yearly['min'], ump_yearly['max'], \n                alpha=0.2, color='#F18F01', label='Range (Min-Max)')\n\nax.set_xlabel('Tahun', fontsize=14, fontweight='bold')\nax.set_ylabel('UMP (Rupiah)', fontsize=14, fontweight='bold')\nax.set_title('Evolusi Upah Minimum Provinsi di Indonesia (2002-2020)', \n             fontsize=16, fontweight='bold', pad=20)\nax.legend(fontsize=12, loc='upper left')\nax.grid(True, alpha=0.3, linestyle='--')\nax.yaxis.set_major_formatter(plt.FuncFormatter(lambda x, p: f'Rp {x/1e6:.1f}M'))\n\n# Tambahkan anotasi untuk poin penting\nfor i, row in ump_yearly.iterrows():\n    if row['tahun'] in [2002, 2020]:\n        ax.annotate(f\"Rp {row['mean']/1e6:.1f}M\", \n                   xy=(row['tahun'], row['mean']), \n                   xytext=(10, 10), textcoords='offset points',\n                   fontsize=10, fontweight='bold',\n                   bbox=dict(boxstyle='round,pad=0.5', facecolor='yellow', alpha=0.7))\n\nplt.tight_layout()\nplt.show()\n\n# Tampilkan tabel\nprint(\"\\n📊 Tabel Evolusi UMP Tahunan:\")\nump_yearly_display = ump_yearly.copy()\nump_yearly_display['mean'] = ump_yearly_display['mean'].apply(lambda x: f'Rp {x:,.0f}')\nump_yearly_display['median'] = ump_yearly_display['median'].apply(lambda x: f'Rp {x:,.0f}')\nump_yearly_display['min'] = ump_yearly_display['min'].apply(lambda x: f'Rp {x:,.0f}')\nump_yearly_display['max'] = ump_yearly_display['max'].apply(lambda x: f'Rp {x:,.0f}')\ndisplay(ump_yearly_display)","metadata":{"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2026-04-06T00:59:54.519405Z","iopub.execute_input":"2026-04-06T00:59:54.520000Z","iopub.status.idle":"2026-04-06T00:59:54.958878Z","shell.execute_reply.started":"2026-04-06T00:59:54.519947Z","shell.execute_reply":"2026-04-06T00:59:54.958052Z"},"trusted":true},"outputs":[{"output_type":"display_data","data":{"text/plain":"<Figure size 1600x800 with 1 Axes>","image/png":"\n"},"metadata":{}},{"name":"stdout","text":"\n📊 Tabel Evolusi UMP Tahunan:\n","output_type":"stream"},{"output_type":"display_data","data":{"t