si UMP Antar Provinsi (2020)","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"# Visualisasi distribusi\nfig, (ax1, ax2) = plt.subplots(1, 2, figsize=(16, 6))\n\n# Histogram\nax1.hist(ump_2020['ump'], bins=20, color='#A23B72', alpha=0.7, edgecolor='black')\nax1.axvline(ump_2020['ump'].mean(), color='red', linestyle='--', linewidth=2, label=f\"Mean: Rp {ump_2020['ump'].mean()/1e6:.2f}M\")\nax1.axvline(ump_2020['ump'].median(), color='green', linestyle='--', linewidth=2, label=f\"Median: Rp {ump_2020['ump'].median()/1e6:.2f}M\")\nax1.set_xlabel('UMP (Rupiah)', fontsize=12, fontweight='bold')\nax1.set_ylabel('Jumlah Provinsi', fontsize=12, fontweight='bold')\nax1.set_title('Distribusi UMP di Indonesia (2020)', fontsize=13, fontweight='bold', pad=15)\nax1.legend(fontsize=10)\nax1.grid(True, alpha=0.3, axis='y')\nax1.xaxis.set_major_formatter(plt.FuncFormatter(lambda x, p: f'Rp {x/1e6:.1f}M'))\n\n# Box plot\nbox = ax2.boxplot([ump_2020['ump']], vert=True, patch_artist=True, widths=0.5)\nbox['boxes'][0].set_facecolor('#2E86AB')\nbox['boxes'][0].set_alpha(0.7)\nax2.set_ylabel('UMP (Rupiah)', fontsize=12, fontweight='bold')\nax2.set_title('Box Plot UMP (2020)', fontsize=13, fontweight='bold', pad=15)\nax2.set_xticklabels(['UMP 2020'])\nax2.yaxis.set_major_formatter(plt.FuncFormatter(lambda x, p: f'Rp {x/1e6:.1f}M'))\nax2.grid(True, alpha=0.3, axis='y')\n\n# Tambahkan anotasi untuk outliers\nQ1 = ump_2020['ump'].quantile(0.25)\nQ3 = ump_2020['ump'].quantile(0.75)\nIQR = Q3 - Q1\noutliers = ump_2020[(ump_2020['ump'] < Q1 - 1.5*IQR) | (ump_2020['ump'] > Q3 + 1.5*IQR)]\n\nfor _, row in outliers.iterrows():\n    ax2.annotate(row['provinsi'], xy=(1, row['ump']), xytext=(1.15, row['ump']),\n                fontsize=8, bbox=dict(boxstyle='round,pad=0.3', facecolor='yellow', alpha=0.7))\n\nplt.tight_layout()\nplt.show()\n\n# Statistik kesenjangan\nprint(\"\\n📊 Analisis Kesenjangan UMP (2020):\")\nprint(\"=\"*80)\nprint(f\"✓ Range UMP: Rp {ump_2020['ump'].min():,.0f} - Rp {ump_2020['ump'].max():,.0f}\")\nprint(f\"✓ Kesenjangan (Max - Min): Rp {ump_2020['ump'].max() - ump_2020['ump'].min():,.0f}\")\nprint(f\"✓ Koefisien Variasi: {(ump_2020['ump'].std() / ump_2020['ump'].mean() * 100):.2f}%\")\nprint(f\"✓ Standar Deviasi: Rp {ump_2020['ump'].std():,.0f}\")\nprint(f\"✓ Q1 (25th percentile): Rp {Q1:,.0f}\")\nprint(f\"✓ Q3 (75th percentile): Rp {Q3:,.0f}\")\nprint(f\"✓ IQR: Rp {IQR:,.0f}\")","metadata":{"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2026-04-06T00:59:56.060377Z","iopub.execute_input":"2026-04-06T00:59:56.060669Z","iopub.status.idle":"2026-04-06T00:59:56.426604Z","shell.execute_reply.started":"2026-04-06T00:59:56.060641Z","shell.execute_reply":"2026-04-06T00:59:56.425767Z"},"trusted":true},"outputs":[{"output_type":"display_data","data":{"text/plain":"<Figure size 1600x600 with 2 Axes>","image/png":"\n"},"metadata":{}},{"name":"stdout","text":"\n📊 Analisis Kesenjangan UMP (2020):\n================================================================================\n✓ Range UMP: Rp 1,704,608 - Rp 4,276,350\n✓ Kesenjangan (Max - Min): Rp 2,571,742\n✓ Koefisien Variasi: 20.31%\n✓ Standar Deviasi: Rp 542,862\n✓ Q1 (25th percentile): Rp 2,415,850\n✓ Q3 (75th percentile): Rp 3,003,132\n✓ IQR: Rp 587,282\n","output_type":"stream"}],"execution_count":14},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"**Interpretasi distribusi dan kesenjangan UMP 2020**\n\nHistogram dan boxplot membantu melihat apakah UMP tersebar merata atau terkonsentrasi pada rentang tertentu. Koefisien variasi sekitar **20%** menunjukkan adanya disparitas yang cukup nyata, meskipun belum dapat dikatakan sangat ekstrem.\n\nSelisih maksimum dan minimum yang mencapai lebih dari **Rp2,5 juta** memperlihatkan bahwa pekerja di provinsi yang berbeda menghadapi standar minimum pengupahan yang sangat berbeda. Ini penting karena UMP pada akhirnya berhubungan dengan daya beli minimum dan biaya hidup regional.\n","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"## 5. Analisis Provinsi Tertentu","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"### 5.1 Perbandingan UMP: DKI Jakarta vs Jawa Barat vs Jawa Timur","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"# Pilih provinsi untuk dibandingkan\nprovinces_to_compare = ['DKI JAKARTA', 'JAWA BARAT', 'JAWA TIMUR', 'BANTEN', 'JAWA TENGAH']\ndf_compare = df_ump[df_ump['provinsi'].isin(provinces_to_compare)]\n\n# Visualisasi\nfig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(16, 8))\n\nfor prov in provinces_to_compare:\n    data = df_compare[df_compare['provinsi'] == prov]\n    ax.plot(data['tahun'], data['ump'], marker='o', linewidth=2.5, label=prov, markersize=6)\n\nax.set_xlabel('Tahun', fontsize=14, fontweight='bold')\nax.set_ylabel('UMP (Rupiah)', fontsize=14, fontweight='bold')\nax.set_title('Perbandingan Evolusi UMP: Provinsi di Pulau Jawa', fontsize=16, fontweight='bold', pad=20)\nax.legend(fontsize=11, loc='upper left')\nax.grid(True, alpha=0.3, linestyle='--')\nax.yaxis.set_major_formatter(plt.FuncFormatter(lambda x, p: f'Rp {x/1e6:.1f}M'))\n\nplt.tight_layout()\nplt.show()\n\n# Hitung growth rate untuk setiap provinsi\nprint(\"\\n📊 Pertumbuhan Kumulatif UMP (2002-2020):\")\nprint(\"=\"*80)\nfor prov in provinces_to_compare:\n    data = df_compare[df_compare['provinsi'] == prov].sort_values('tahun')\n    if len(data) > 0:\n        first_val = data.iloc[0]['ump']\n        last_val = data.iloc[-1]['ump']\n        growth = ((last_val / first_val) - 1) * 100\n        print(f\"{prov:20} | Rp {first_val:>12,} → Rp {last_val:>12,} | Growth: {growth:>7.2f}%\")","metadata":{"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2026-04-06T00:59:56.427635Z","iopub.execute_input":"2026-04-06T00:59:56.427945Z","iopub.status.idle":"2026-04-06T00:59:56.744425Z","shell.execute_reply.started":"2026-04-06T00:59:56.427918Z","shell.execute_reply":"2026-04-06T00:59:56.743291Z"},"trusted":true},"outputs":[{"output_type":"display_data","data":{"text/plain":"<Figure size 1600x800 with 1 Axes>","image/png":"\n"},"metadata":{}},{"name":"stdout","text":"\n📊 Pertumbuhan Kumulatif UMP (2002-2020):\n================================================================================\nDKI JAKARTA          | Rp    591,300.0 → Rp  4,641,854.0 | Growth:  685.03%\nJAWA BARAT           | Rp    280,800.0 → Rp  1,841,487.0 | Growth:  555.80%\nJAWA TIMUR           | Rp    245,000.0 → Rp  1,891,567.0 | Growth:  672.07%\nBANTEN               | Rp    360,000.0 → Rp  2,501,203.0 | Growth:  594.78%\nJAWA TENGAH          | Rp    314,500.0 → Rp  1,812,935.0 | Growth:  476.45%\n","output_type":"stream"}],"execution_count":15},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"**Interpretasi perbandingan provinsi di Pulau Jawa**\n\nPerbandingan antarprovinsi di Jawa menunjukkan bahwa **DKI Jakarta** berada pada level yang paling tinggi hampir sepanjang periode pengamatan. Ini sejalan dengan posisinya sebagai pusat ekonomi nasional dengan biaya hidup yang lebih mahal dibanding provinsi lain.\n\nMenariknya, meskipun level awal dan akhirnya berbeda, seluruh provinsi yang dibandingkan tetap memperlihatkan pertumbuhan kumulatif yang tinggi. Artinya, kenaikan UMP tidak hanya terjadi di daerah termaju, tetapi juga menyebar ke provinsi lain di Pulau Jawa.\n","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"### 5.2 Heatmap UMP Provinsi (2015-2020)","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"# Pivot data untuk heatmap (hanya 2015-2020 agar tidak terlalu padat)\nump_recent = df_ump[df_ump['tahun'] >= 2015]\nump_pivot = ump_recent.pivot(index='provinsi', columns='tahun', values='ump')\n\n# Sort berdasarkan UMP 2020\nump_pivot = ump_pivot.sort_values(2020, ascending=False)\n\n# Visualisasi heatmap\nfig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(12, 16))\n\nsns.heatmap(ump_pivot, annot=True, fmt='.0f', cmap='YlOrRd', \n            cbar_kws={'label': 'UMP (Rupiah)'}, linewidths=0.5, ax=ax)\n\nax.set_title('Heatmap UMP Seluruh Provinsi (2015-2020)', fontsize=16, fontweight='bold', pad=20)\nax.set_xlabel('Tahun', fontsize=12, fontweight='bold')\nax.set_ylabel('Provinsi', fontsize=12, fontweight='bold')\n\nplt.tight_layout()\np