,"execution_count":22},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"**Interpretasi pengelompokan region**\n\nPengelompokan region membantu menyederhanakan analisis dari level provinsi ke level kawasan. Dengan pendekatan ini, kita bisa melihat apakah ketimpangan upah lebih banyak terjadi **antarprovinsi di dalam satu kawasan** atau **antarwilayah besar di Indonesia**.\n\n","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"### 8.2 Perbandingan UMP Antar Region","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"# Filter tahun 2020\nump_2020_region = df_ump[df_ump['tahun'] == 2020].copy()\n\n# Visualisasi boxplot per region\nfig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(16, 8))\n\nregions_order = ['Jawa-Bali', 'Sumatera', 'Kalimantan', 'Sulawesi', 'Maluku-Papua', 'Nusa Tenggara']\ndata_to_plot = [ump_2020_region[ump_2020_region['region'] == r]['ump'].values for r in regions_order]\n\nbox = ax.boxplot(data_to_plot, labels=regions_order, patch_artist=True, widths=0.6)\n\n# Warnai box\ncolors = ['#2E86AB', '#A23B72', '#F18F01', '#C73E1D', '#6A994E', '#BC4B51']\nfor patch, color in zip(box['boxes'], colors):\n    patch.set_facecolor(color)\n    patch.set_alpha(0.7)\n\nax.set_ylabel('UMP (Rupiah)', fontsize=14, fontweight='bold')\nax.set_xlabel('Region', fontsize=14, fontweight='bold')\nax.set_title('Distribusi UMP per Region (2020)', fontsize=16, fontweight='bold', pad=20)\nax.yaxis.set_major_formatter(plt.FuncFormatter(lambda x, p: f'Rp {x/1e6:.1f}M'))\nax.grid(True, alpha=0.3, axis='y')\nplt.xticks(rotation=15)\n\nplt.tight_layout()\nplt.show()\n\n# Statistik per region\nprint(\"\\n📊 Statistik UMP per Region (2020):\")\nprint(\"=\"*100)\nregion_stats = ump_2020_region.groupby('region')['ump'].agg(['mean', 'median', 'std', 'min', 'max'])\nregion_stats = region_stats.sort_values('mean', ascending=False)\nfor col in ['mean', 'median', 'std', 'min', 'max']:\n    region_stats[col] = region_stats[col].apply(lambda x: f'Rp {x:,.0f}')\ndisplay(region_stats)","metadata":{"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2026-0